00030     int stall_count;        /**< the max number of 4-swap kicks to perform
00031                                  without making progress */
00032     int kicks;              /**< the number of 4-swap kicks to perform */
00033     int kick_type;          /**< the type of kick: one of CC_LK_RANDOM_KICK,

00035                                  see Concorde documentation for more info */
00036     double time_bound;      /**< stop after this running time reached; set to 
00037                                  0 to have no time bound, must be positive */
00038     double length_bound;    /**< stop after finding tour of this length; must

00040     int *initial_tour;      /**< initial tour (may be NULL) */
00041 } arrow_tsp_cc_lk_params;

00068  *  @brief  Sets default parameters for Lin-Kernighan heuristic:
00069  *              - random_restarts = 0
